local this = UIComponent(Address)
function ShowMenu(name) for i = 0, this:ChildCount() - 1 do local child = UIComponent(this:Find(i)) child:SetVisible(child:Id() == name) end end

state.unicode: Capture 20 enemy vessels in honest, manly battle against the foe!

Command stars display a player's ranking. || They are awarded through the accumulation of skill points. || A player's command stars will be displayed in the multiplayer lobby. || Seek out an opponent with a similar ranking, or challenge one with a higher ranking for a challenge and the potential to gain further skill points.

Your skill rating is a way of gauging your battle prowess against that of other players. || You receive skill points for each ranked or drop-in battle you play. || Your skill rating determines how many command stars you hold and your ranking. || The higher ranking your opponent has, the more points you will be awarded for victory!
